ActSpecies at Risk Act
SubjectEmergency Order for the Protection of the Western Chorus Frog (Great Lakes / St. Lawrence — Canadian Shield Population)
PrecisEMERGENCY ORDER FOR THE PROTECTION OF THE WESTERN CHORUS FROG (GREAT LAKES / ST. LAWRENCE - CANADIAN SHIELD POPULATION (GLSLCS)) in order to provide protection to the Western Chorus Frog (GLSLCS) by addressing the imminent threat to its recovery, including by protecting the habitat identified in the Order to stabilize the metapopulation and help the recovery of the species.
